==English==
===Etymology===
''Pot'' in the sense of a small glass of beer, though the term applies for any alcoholic drink.

===Noun===
'''[[two]] [[pot]] [[screamer]]'''
# {{AU}} {{colloquial}} A person who becomes [[intoxicated]] or rowdy after drinking just a relatively small amount of [[alcohol]].  (Reference: Australian National Dictionary Centre at the [[w:Austrlian National University|Austrlian National University]] [http://www.anu.edu.au/andc/res/aewords/aewords_sz.php].)